description: I invited Stock Idol winner JP to congratulate him on his new title and give him a gift for us all to enjoy, a brand new Fleshlight. Of course I asked him to try it in front of us and to fuck the Fleshlight mount. A joy to watch! JP really wanted to win this popularity contest. Glad he chose us to celebrate his victory!  Congrats JP!
title: 2015 Stock Idol Winner, Scene #01
